===Etymology 1===
From {{cog|trk-pro|*yạp-}}.
====Verb====
{{head|az|verb}} {{tlb|az|transitive}}
#  to [[stick]] or [[attach]] something onto a flat and vertical surface {{q|such as flatbread dough onto the inner walls of a [[tandoor]]}}
=====Conjugation=====
{{az-latin-conj|a}}
=====Derived terms=====
